item.title: Hawkish Australian Economists See RBA Raising Key Rate to 4.6%
item.description: RBA to Raise Cash Rate to 4.6%? A group of Australian economists are predicting that the Reserve Bank of Australia (RBA) will raise the cash rate to 4.6% by the end of 2023. This would be the highest level for the cash rate since 1994.
